{"tid":257659,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【經典劏場】首都廣場勁蝕92%售出 旺中大業主子70萬接貨","createTime":"2017-05-25T12:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T14:14:19.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"169be9b7a593727bb7ff7b971f994195d309fbbf","tid":257659,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495706782_0b2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495706782_0b2d.jpg&h=accd40ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495706784_7407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495706784_7407.jpg&h=6446a01c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典劏場尖沙嘴首都廣場，續現大幅蝕讓個案。根據土地註冊處資料顯示，首都廣場1樓F148號舖，建築面積160方呎，實用面積80方呎，在上月底以70萬元登記售出，實用呎價8,750元。<br />\n<br />\n單位於2013年底以827.2萬元一手賣出，由一名陳姓及一名吳姓買家聯名持有。不過，至2015年商場入伙後，該吳姓買家以150萬元購入全部業權，舖位已大幅貶值81.9%。如今吳姓買家亦棄守舖位，以70萬元售出，賬面蝕80萬元，但卻較4年前一手價，大幅貶值757.2萬元，勁蝕91.5%。以一手價計，為商場史上蝕得最勁舖位。<br />\n<br />\n翻查舖位紀錄，由一手購入至今，舖位未曾向任何財務機構借錢，有理由相信舖位全由現金Full Pay購入。<br />\n<br />\n而新買家卻有名堂，為資深投資者余國銓的兒子余旻駿，料是次以超低價吸納舖位搏升值。余國銓主力投資舖位，在多個劏場如旺角中心、旺角好景商場等都有舖位收租，他更屬旺角中心商場大業主。<br />\n<br />\n而連同上址在內共28個舖位，剛以3.8萬元合併租出。以業權比例分配，此舖每月可袋3,139元租金，以最新成交價70萬元計算，回報率高達5.4厘，回報較一般舖位多超過一倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56741691&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56741691%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170525&d=UpCGnSyyXP1JUvkUpR2X9TACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=9e9e8413\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56741691%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170525&h=f3c31a12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56741691&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170525</a>"},{"pid":"a2c62f9788cffbe7efd44ee56a150f9b8c24e268","tid":257659,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"Full pay 都賣？持貨力咁強，點解要平買？"},{"pid":"f62a9ad155eb89f239528c381ed27813cb5f5dfa","tid":257659,"uid":42229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"無知一問 其實60萬 抵唔抵買 平租出去等長線博收購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192a706d66768031fe687dc75be56326ac566e68","tid":257659,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T14:14:19.000Z","msg":"70萬平到笑<br />\n19車位都唔止<br />\n呢個數買到尖沙咀甫位 緊係值"}]}